  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1726290/extras/9ca066d64539673faf8f619728f36882.poster.avif?t=1648663910\" width=624 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1726290/extras/9ca066d64539673faf8f619728f36882.webm?t=1648663910\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1726290/extras/9ca066d64539673faf8f619728f36882.mp4?t=1648663910\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>-The evil necromancer, who sought the fall of all kingdoms on The Continent - Zuldan, has been brought back to life by his loyal servants. Only the Middle Kingdom- Murgaz, remained after barely defeating Zuldan and is now the home of all who survived his wrath. Take part in the battle as King Severin protect your kingdom.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Build your own defense: Each part of the kingdom requires a different strategy to be defended, so you will need to place the towers carefully.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1726290/extras/a4acea7190cac9cae793198bf42423f5.poster.avif?t=1648663910\" width=668 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1726290/extras/a4acea7190cac9cae793198bf42423f5.webm?t=1648663910\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1726290/extras/a4acea7190cac9cae793198bf42423f5.mp4?t=1648663910\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li>Use the unique abilities of the mages: Each tower has a unique attribute and ability - make good use of it and oppose the assault!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1726290/extras/055a501315db5293ea7615c27a3a180e.poster.avif?t=1648663910\" width=746 height=242 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1726290/extras/055a501315db5293ea7615c27a3a180e.webm?t=1648663910\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1726290/extras/055a501315db5293ea7615c27a3a180e.mp4?t=1648663910\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li>Follow the narrative: The Last Defense is the first part of a trilogy and the beginning of the story. Stay tuned with ThuGGames for more.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1726290/extras/e73fea351cb66fc37aa4fb8c88750f79.poster.avif?t=1648663910\" width=518 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1726290/extras/e73fea351cb66fc37aa4fb8c88750f79.webm?t=1648663910\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1726290/extras/e73fea351cb66fc37aa4fb8c88750f79.mp4?t=1648663910\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></li></ul>",
